(Scalar multiplication closure.) If for all 
\begin_inset Formula $i\in I$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $v\in V_{i}$
\end_inset

, then for call 
\begin_inset Formula $c\in\mathbb{F}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $cv\in V_{i}$
\end_inset

, so 
