\begin_inset Formula $U_{1}+U_{2}:=\{u_{1}+u_{2}:u_{1}\in U_{1},u_{2}\in U_{2}\}=\{u_{2}+u_{1}:u_{1}\in U_{1},u_{2}\in U_{2}\}=U_{2}+U_{1}$
